    "client_msg_id": "7916c5b2-d81e-4023-a14f-6f0e86d45fd5",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "While I haven't seen any released *software* artifacts from STEPS, I've been recently impressed by Alan Kay's demo of an old system from PARC: <https://youtu.be/AnrlSqtpOkw?t=3m27s> which they ran on top of a hardware emulator in javascript (available here: <https://lively-web.org/users/bert/Smalltalk-78.html>)\n\nApparently this whole system is/was about 10KLOC (above the hardware).",
